<p class=indbig>
<b>Introducing Mac OS 8.
Superior performance, Multi-tasking,
Unparalleled customization, Integrated Internet tools.
Out of this world.</b>
</p><p class=indbig>
<b>An operating system so advanced it could only come from Apple. (Or did it?)</b>
</p><p class=indbig>
Get ready for a close encounter of the eighth kind. Mac&reg; OS 8 is here. And with 
it comes a whole new way of working with your Mac OS computer.
</p><p class=indbig>
Mac OS 8&rsquo;s purpose on this planet is to help you work more productively, 
and remove the barriers between you and your full potential. And it does 
this with performance that&rsquo;s out of this world. Thanks to the Mac OS 8 
improved multi-tasking Finder&trade; software, you can accomplish several tasks at 
once, like opening and copying files without any waiting around. But all 
this power is nothing without organization. That&rsquo;s why its new unparalleled 
customization features let you adapt your system to match your individual 
work style. Spring-open folders, contextual menus and pop-up windows help get you 
around faster, and are part of a new 3-dimensional look that&rsquo;s even easier 
to work with. And Mac OS 8 has integrated Internet capabilities.
Netscape Navigator&trade;, the PointCast Network, Internet Explorer and a 
new Internet Setup Assistant are built right in, making it easier than ever to get 
on the Net, to email, surf or browse the cosmos<sup><small>*</small></sup>. All this 
lets you work the way you think, so you can be more efficient. It even includes 
QuickTime&reg; multimedia technology. And to show that Mac OS 8 comes in peace, 
it can read Windows files, whether you have the original application or not. It&rsquo;s 
also compatible with your existing Mac applications. Mac OS 8 is designed for 
68040 and PowerPC&trade;-based systems, and features reliability improvements 
that&rsquo;ll have you glad you went with the power of 8.
</p><p class=indbig>
Intelligent life is out there. And Mac OS 8 is proof.
</p><p class=indbig>
For your own close encounter with Mac OS 8, visit http://macos.apple.com for 
a list of local software resellers or a free demo. Or give us a ring at
1-800-482-6376 ext 1558.
</p><p class=indbig>
<b>What a difference 8 makes.</b>
</p>
